e%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20going%20to%20include%20a%20picture%20of%20an%20empty%20baguette%20holder%2C%20but%20then%20I%20found%20this%20one%20from%20the%20car's%20launch%20showing%20Olympic%20gold%20medal-winning%20British%20diver%20Tom%20Daley%20with%20an%20actual%20baguette%20in%20the%20holder%20instead.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20could%20also%20use%20the%20holder%20for%20a%20bunch%20of%20flowers%2C%20should%20you%20be%20so%20inclined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227085%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tom%20Daley%20in%20a%20Renault%205%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685e878ef748d8c055f47d2e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225021%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBritish%20Olympic%20diver%20Tom%20Daley%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20baguette%20%E2%80%94%20in%20a%20Renault%205.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Pepler%2FPinPep%2FRenault%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20might%20have%20guessed%20from%20the%20E%2C%20the%20revived%205%20is%20indeed%20electric%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20gas%20equivalent.%20It%20came%20about%20after%20now-departing%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-ceo-gucci-kering-luca-de-meo-renault-turnaround-stock-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELuca%20de%20Meo%3C%2Fa%3E%20rashly%20promised%20in%20a%20speech%20that%20Renault%20could%20make%20a%20new%20car%20in%20just%2024%20months%20%E2%80%94%20a%20very%20tight%20timeline%20in%20the%20auto%20world%20%E2%80%94%20and%20managed%20to%20do%20so%20only%20a%20few%20weeks%20past%20that%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%205%20made%20its%20debut%20way%20back%20in%201972%20and%20was%20an%20instant%20hit%2C%20becoming%20the%20best-selling%20car%20in%20France%20for%2014%20years%2C%20with%20about%205.5%20million%20vehicles%20sold%20during%20that%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224096%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lady%20Diana%20Spencer's%20Renault%205%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685e98a63d5881a51c1c36b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222731%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELady%20Diana%20Spencer%20owned%20a%20Renault%205%20before%20she%20married%20Prince%20Charles.%20She%20got%20a%20parking%20ticket%20in%201980.%3Cp%3EPA%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20was%20available%20in%20the%20US%20in%20the%20late%201970s%2C%20as%20Le%20Car%2C%20it%20didn't%20exactly%20bewitch%20American%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouped-up%20versions%20appealed%20to%20boy%20racers%2C%20and%20a%20turbo%20model%20won%20the%20Monte%20Carlo%20Rally%20in%201981.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%205%20is%20Europe's%20car%20of%20the%20year%202025%2C%20beating%20the%20Alfa%20Romeo%20Junior%2C%20Citro%C3%ABn%20C3-%C3%ABC3%2C%20Cupra%20Terramar%2C%20Dacia%20Duster%2C%20Hyundai%20Inster%20and%20Kia%20EV3.%20It%20was%20back-to-back%20wins%20for%20Renault%2C%20after%20the%20Scenic%20%E2%80%94%20a%20small%20MPV%20%E2%80%94%20took%20the%20crown%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20out%20why%20the%205%20won%2C%20I%20took%20a%20train%20on%20a%20very%20warm%20Friday%20afternoon%20earlier%20this%20month%20to%20the%20northern%20edge%20of%20London%20to%20pick%20up%20an%20R5.%20It%20had%20a%2052kWh%20battery%2C%20150%20HP%20engine%2C%20and%20came%20in%20vibrant%20%26quot%3BPop!%20Green.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20this%20car%20would%20set%20you%20back%20a%20shade%20under%20%C2%A327%2C000%20(%2436%2C300)%2C%20and%20has%20a%20decent%20WLTP%20range%20of%20251%20miles.%20This%20configuration%20represents%20the%20best%20value%20for%20money%2C%20according%20to%20What%20Car%3F%20The%20range%20starts%20at%20about%20%C2%A323%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hit%20the%20M40%20motorway%20bound%20for%20the%20picturesque%20town%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-hidden-gems-in-uk-that-everyone-should-visit-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStratford-upon-Avon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20birthplace%20of%20William%20Shakespeare.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20do%20the%20speed%20limit%20of%2070%20miles%20an%20hour%20for%20most%20of%20the%20journey%20and%20got%20there%20in%20about%20two%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20failed%20to%20connect%20my%20iPhone%20to%20the%20audio%20system%20before%20setting%20off%2C%20I%20tuned%20into%20the%20top%2040%20singles%20countdown%20on%20BBC%20Radio%201%20%E2%80%94%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsabrina-carpenter-new-album-cover-mans-best-friend-rolling-stone-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESabrina%20Carpenter%3C%2Fa%3E%20ended%20Alex%20Warren's%2012-week%20run%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20chart%2C%20by%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20audio%20system%20sounds%20superb%20%E2%80%94%20and%20was%20apparently%20created%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhistleblower-edward-snowden-artist-jean-michel-jarre-making-techno-song-exit-nsa-surveillance-2016-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJean-Michel%20Jarre%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20legendary%20French%20electronic%20music%20artist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Renault%205%20audio%20system%20display%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685e73493d5881a51c1c3479%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Renault%205's%20audio%20system%20was%20created%20by%20Jean-Michel%20Jarre.%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20small-ish%20EV%2C%20the%205%20packs%20a%20punch%2C%20doing%20the%20speed%20limit%20effortlessly%20with%20plenty%20in%20reserve%2C%20had%20I%20wanted%20to%20risk%20a%20speeding%20fine.%20I%20can't%20say%20it's%20the%20quietest%20car%20I've%20ever%20driven%2C%20but%20I%20can't%20fault%20the%20ride%20and%20handling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20well%20as%20the%20baguette%20holder%2C%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20charming%2Fweird%20touches%2C%20such%20as%20the%20%26quot%3B5%26quot%3B%20battery%20indicator%20on%20the%20hood%20that%20lights%20up.%20It's%20part%20of%20the%20car's%20%26quot%3Bmodern%20lighting%20signature%20with%20cheeky%20welcome%20and%20goodbye%20sequences%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Renault%20puts%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20illuminated%20battery%20indicator%20on%20the%20Renault%205's%20hood.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685e8a8a3d5881a51c1c356b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20illuminated%20battery%20indicator%20on%20the%20Renault%205's%20hood.%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%205%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20fun%20to%20drive%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-ev-mg-mg4-test-drive-tesla-byd-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Equite%20boring%20MG%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20tested%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Not%20everyone%20may%20love%20its%20many%20quirks%2C%20such%20as%20the%20fabric%20on%20the%20dashboard%20and%20ceiling%2C%20and%20I%20found%20the%20four%E2%80%94yes%2C%20four%E2%80%94control%20stalks%20plus%20controls%20on%20the%20steering%20wheel%20to%20be%20quite%20bewildering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20I'm%20just%20easily%20confused%2C%20but%20I%20still%20failed%20to%20master%20the%20automatic%20transmission%20before%20having%20to%20give%20the%20car%20back.%20And%20I%20still%20have%20no%20idea%20what%20the%20%26quot%3BMulti-Sense%26quot%3B%20button%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225818%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Renault%205%20dashboard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685e8d07f748d8c055f47d8e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223273%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20found%20the%20automatic%20transmission%20on%20the%20Renault%205%20somewhat%20baffling.%3Cp%3ERenault%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20about%2050%25%20left%20and%20didn't%20want%20to%20risk%20running%20out%20of%20charge%20on%20the%20trip%20back%20to%20London%2C%20so%20I%20found%20a%20charging%20station%20in%20a%20fairly%20dismal%20retail%20park%20in%20Banbury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20actually%20the%20first%20time%20I've%20charged%20an%20EV%2C%20and%20it%20took%20me%20a%20minute%20to%20work%20out%20the%20right%20plug%20(yes%2C%20I%20am%20a%20slow%20learner).%20Fortunately%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20create%20an%20account%20to%20use%20the%20charger%20and%20could%20just%20tap%20my%20credit%20card%20to%20release%20the%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20the%20charge%20up%20to%20about%2080%25%20took%20about%2015%20minutes%20and%20cost%20just%20over%20%C2%A315%20(about%20%2420).%20Public%20chargers%20are%20not%20that%20cheap%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20had%20the%20car%20been%20close%20to%20flat%2C%20it%20would've%20set%20me%20back%20about%20%C2%A350%20(almost%20%2470)%20to%20reach%20100%25%20%E2%80%94%20not%20too%20much%20less%20than%20a%20tank%20of%20gas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20garage%20or%20driveway%2C%20the%20economics%20of%20an%20EV%20become%20considerably%20more%20complicated%2C%20which%20is%20one%20reason%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhonda-hybrids-ev-electric-vehicles-pivot-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehybrids%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20popular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Renault%205%20at%20a%20charger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685e8ec0f748d8c055f47dab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECharging%20the%20Renault%205%20was%20reasonably%20painless.%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20the%205%20E-Tech%20was%20the%20UK's%20best-selling%20EV%20for%20retail%20buyers.%20In%20both%20April%20and%20May%2C%20it%20helped%20Renault%20take%20the%20top%20spot%20for%20private%20registrations%20of%20pure%20EVs.%20According%20to%20Renaul