or%20me.%20What%20I%20took%20issue%20with%20the%20most%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-1-million-giveaway-legal-questions-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egiveaway%20for%20prospective%20voters%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20seemed%20so%20morally%20wrong.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20actively%20looking%20into%20his%20history%2C%20and%20the%20company's.%20The%20stock%20price%20and%20how%20we're%20making%20money%20%E2%80%94%20none%20of%20it%20made%20sense%20to%20me.%20That%20was%20another%20reason%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20out.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20empty%20promises%20that%20haven't%20been%20fulfilled%2C%20like%20Full%20Self-Driving%20or%20the%20lower-cost%20EV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221bcead9b-c4fa-4607-be0b-dba04433c8a2%5C%22%3EWhen%20I%20first%20left%2C%20I%20gave%20myself%20a%20hard%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20lifted%20his%20arm%20and%20did%20that%20Nazi%20salute%2C%20I%20was%20disgusted.%20%3Cem%3E(Editor's%20note%3A%20While%20discussing%20the%20incident%20with%20Joe%20Rogan%2C%20Musk%20said%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-key-points-elon-musk-interview-joe-rogan-doge-ai-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BHopefully%2C%20people%20realize%20I'm%20not%20a%20Nazi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%20Last%20year%2C%20I%20started%20to%20be%20ashamed%20to%20tell%20people%20where%20I%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chatted%20with%20a%20couple%20of%20folks%20at%20Tesla%20and%20I%20explained%20to%20them%20why%20I%20believed%20that%20that%20was%20a%20Nazi%20salute%2C%20and%20most%20of%20the%20time%20they%20just%20heard%20me%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENear%20the%20end%20of%20my%20time%20at%20Tesla%2C%20I%20started%20bringing%20up%20politics%20because%20I'd%20kind%20of%20got%20to%20a%20point%20where%20I%20didn't%20really%20care.%20I%20started%20working%20on