us%20kitchens%2C%20ample%20outdoor%20space%2C%20and%20smart%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHigh%20home%20prices%20and%20elevated%20mortgage%20rates%20have%20made%20homebuyers%20keenly%20aware%20of%20what%20features%20add%20the%20most%20value%20to%20their%20daily%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20Quint%20said.%20%26quot%3BBuyers%20have%20determined%20that%20investing%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%20in%20a%20patio%2C%20and%20home%20security%20features%20enhances%20the%20livability%20of%20a%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NAHB's%20survey%2C%20here%20are%20four%20trends%20shaping%20homebuying%20%E2%80%94%20from%20a%20bigger%20kitchen%20that%20focuses%20on%20efficiency%20to%20smart%20thermostats%20that%20allow%20homeowners%20to%20control%20their%20home's%20temperature%20remotely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E1.%20Buyers%20want%20a%20bigger%20kitchen.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20family%20gathered%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20A%20man%2C%20small%20child%20and%20woman%20look%20at%20each%20other.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685ae3903d5881a51c1bfd3c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223758%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENewly%20built%20homes%20are%20shrinking%2C%20but%20kitchens%20are%20getting%20larger%20proportionally.%3Cp%3EMaskot%2FGetty%20Images%2FMaskot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-dream-shrinking-smaller-homes-fewer-kids-vacation-time-commutes-2024-12%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%25202015%252C%2520new%2520homes%2520peaked%2Cto%2520about%25202%252C180%2520square%2520feet.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20home%20may%20be%20shrinking%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20one%20space%20buyers%20aren't%20willing%20to%20give%20up%20is%20the%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20those%20buying%20a%20smaller%20house%2C%20if%20that's%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20make%20the%20math%20work%2C%20we%20ask%3A%20What%2