5C%22%3E'I've%20never%20had%20this%20much%20downtime%20in%20June'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20doing%20drag%20over%20a%20decade%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20around%20the%20same%20time%20as%20Holly%20Box-Springs%2C%20actually.%20And%20I've%20seen%20the%20highs%20and%20lows.%20This%20year%20feels%20especially%20slow.%20I've%20never%20had%20this%20much%20downtime%20in%20June%20since%20I%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20year%20long%2C%20at%20least%20twice%20a%20month%2C%20I%20fly%20all%20over%20the%20US%20to%20perform%20%E2%80%94%20Alabama%2C%20Boston%2C%20Seattle%2C%20Denver%2C%20Detroit%2C%20Atlanta%2C%20Hawaii.%20Usually%20I'd%20fly%20out%20on%20a%20Thursday%2C%20do%20a%20show%20on%20a%20Friday%20or%20Saturday%2C%20and%20fly%20back%20by%20Sunday%20for%20my%20regular%20set%20at%20a%20bar%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20during%20Pride%2C%20drag%20queens%20are%20like%20Santa%20Claus%20during%20Christmas%20%E2%80%94%20everyone%20wants%20to%20book%20them%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20typical%20week%20leading%20up%20to%20New%20York%20City%20Pride%20used%20to%20be%20nonstop%20for%20me.%20In%202019%2C%20during%20World%20Pride%2C%20I%20worked%2043%20days%20in%20a%20row%20%E2%80%94%20no%20breaks.%20I%20was%20hired%20by%20big%20companies.%20Some%20days%2C%20I%20had%20multiple%20gigs%2C%20back%20to%20back.%20I%20kept%20count%20because%20it%20was%20the%20year%20I%20filmed%20%26quot%3BRuPaul's%20Drag%20Race.%26quot%3B%20In%20one%20month%20alone%2C%20I%20made%20enough%20money%20to%20buy%20a%20brand%20new%20Toyota%20Prius.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%3F%20I%20only%20have%20eight%20gigs%20total%20for%20the%20month.%20It's%20a%20complete%20180.%20I%20used%20to%20have%20a%20manager%2C%20assistant%2C%20and%20publicist%2C%20but%20I've%20been%20doing%20it%20on%20my%20own%20for%20the%20past%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221158%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brita%20Filter%20drag%20queen%20in%20NYC%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3