0change%20impacts%2C%20including%20more%20frequent%20and%20severe%20droughts%2C%20heatwaves%2C%20and%20rainfall%E2%80%9D.%20The%20people%20across%20India%E2%80%99s%20rural%20pockets%20have%20a%20bone%20to%20pick%20with%20it%3B%20the%20shifting%20seasons%20have%20heralded%20uncertainty%20into%20their%20lives.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20paddy%20farmers%20who%20bear%20the%20brunt%20%E2%80%94%20rice%20covers%2069%20percent%20of%20the%20cultivable%20area%3B%20unseasonal%20rains%20incapacitate%20their%20farming%20patterns.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20harvest%20these%20days%20is%20less%20than%20half%20of%20what%20they%20previously%20achieved%2C%E2%80%9D%20Soumya%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20is%20clear%3A%20despite%20India%E2%80%99s%20hinterland%20experiencing%20some%20semblance%20of%20a%20climate%20crisis%2C%20many%20lack%20the%20vocabulary%20to%20articulate%20it.%20And%20it%20is%20not%20their%20fault%2C%20says%20Jagadish%20Thaker%2C%20a%20senior%20lecturer%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Queensland%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20principal%20investigator%20of%20a%202023%20survey%20by%20the%20Yale%20Program%20on%20Climate%20Change%20Communication%20(YPCCC)%2C%20which%20indicated%20that%20more%20than%2090%20percent%20of%20Indians%20are%20concerned%20about%20global%20warming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20opinion%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20lack%20of%20awareness%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20people%20are%20not%20worried%20about%20it%20%5Bclimate%20change%5D.%20It%20means%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20that%20it%20is%20called%20global%20warming%20and%20that%20it%20is%20caused%20by%20human%20activities.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20bridging%20this%20ecological%20literacy%20chasm%20are%20youth%20li